MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2007-1136. Jennings v. Xenia Twp. Bd. of Zoning Appeals.

Greene App. No. 07-CA-16, 2007-Ohio-2355. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
